				<div class="post single_post" id="post-141500">
			<div class="post_header snap_nopreview"><a href="http://www.crunchgear.com/2010/02/22/science-vindicates-afternoon-naps-yet-again/" rel="bookmark" title="Science vindicates afternoon naps, yet again">Science vindicates afternoon naps, yet again</a></div>
				<div class="post_subheader" style="padding-bottom: 8px;">
															<div class="excerpt_subheader_right">
							<ul>
								<li>
									<a href="#comments" rel="nofollow"><span class="dsq-postid" rel="141500 http://www.crunchgear.com/?p=141500"></span></a>
								</li>
								<li>
									<div>
										<script type="text/javascript">
